        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>Document collection (Days 2–5)</h3>
          <p>2 years of personal &amp; business tax returns, 12–24 months of bank statements, P&amp;L statement, all 1099-NEC forms from AMCs and lender clients, state credential/license verification, E&amp;O insurance proof, and credit pull.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>Income analysis &amp; pre-approval (Days 5–10)</h3>
          <p>We run Form 1084 cash flow analysis on your Schedule C with proper add-backs. If tax-return path doesn't work, we pivot to bank statement or P&amp;L program. Issue pre-approval letter with the exact loan amount and program.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
